metadata.name: Musical Melancholy in the Cutter #1/123
metadata.description:
Sketched on pencil and parchment paper, post production done digitally. An image portraying three close friends lost at sea.

Give way, give way, strings to salt we pull.  
This token may take you places you haven't imagined. 
Jump to the bow from concrete collisions. 
Water logged boots, yeah, sailing gale, as sea birds arc in drooping tracks. 
Muddled minds and softened hearts, soaked to the bone.
